{"tid":886003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗議輕放性騷擾主管 Google全球1500人罷工大遊行","createTime":"2018-11-01T19:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T09:42:11.000Z","uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5d5c3969f10264ee7735746f9b6b75ddfa52f4ac","tid":886003,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T19:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3663/d3663637.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3663%2Fd3663637.jpg&h=a3de57b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於不滿公司對性騒擾處理不公，紐約市的Google員工周四發動罷工大遊行。<br />\n<br />\n網路搜尋引擎巨擘Google旗下Android部門前主管魯賓(Andy Rubin)爆出性騷擾醜聞後，竟然還獲得公司支付巨額資遣費。事件曝光後引爆巨大爭議。全球各地逾1500名員工周四(1日)發起「Google罷工」(Google Walkout)抗議活動。<br />\n<br />\n參加的大部分都是女員工，當中不乏來自東京、新加坡等多個Google的亞洲辦公室。參加的員工紛紛把相關照片與資訊PO到推特與IG，並加上#GoogleWalkout的標籤。<br />\n<br />\n參與罷工的Youtube產品市場經理史達比頓說：「Google以它獨特的工作文化而知名。但如今我們處於不平等的地位、甚至不再獲得應有的尊重。」<br />\n<br />\n罷工發起人要求Google能回應性騷擾事件，同時提出5項具體改革措施：包括要求公司停止以仲裁方式調解性騷擾、承諾終止薪資與機會不平等、公開性侵或性騷擾醜聞報告、提供一個安全途徑讓員工通報遭性侵或性騷擾、同時允許「首席多元化官員」(chief diversity officer)可直接跟執行長對話，向董事會提出意見，並且讓一名員工代表進入董事會。<br />\n<br />\n另有報導指出，Google執行長皮蔡周二曾發送內部郵件給員工，表明會准許和支持員工發起的罷工示威，必要時部門經理亦會提供協助。皮蔡在郵件中重申：Google會回應員工的訴求，對於公司稍早前的回應感到抱歉，認為這不足以平息員工不滿。<br />\n<br />\n目前Google面臨嚴重內部分裂。女性員工除了不滿公司對性騷擾醜聞的處理手法，更抗議公司的職場文化，女性在公司受到不平等對待。只有26%女性員工擔任高層職位，同時女員工薪酬過低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ETxP3l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ETxP3l&d=J6RhEfzMus7NitM9hdRZVDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=b2a677c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ETxP3l</a>"},{"pid":"866337ae2a677c4ba46a4df205d011510ddcaad8","tid":886003,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T19:13:03.000Z","msg":"要求女求職者除衫按摩　Google高層涉性騷擾辭職<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20181101/photo/bkn-20181101090351963-1101_00972_001_01p.jpg?20181101215653\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20181101%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181101090351963-1101_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20181101215653&h=8986d74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRich DeVaul<br />\n<br />\n互聯網巨擘Google旗下Android部門前主管捲入性醜聞，並獲Google支付巨額離職費，引起軒然大波。Google的「X Lab」主管於周二（10月30日）亦因性騷擾指控而離職，但未獲支付離職費。Google行政總裁披差承認，作為行政總裁需採取更強硬態度應對職場性騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n今次捲入性醜聞的是Google秘密實驗室X Lab主管德沃爾（Rich DeVaul），惟Google拒絕透露德沃爾的離職詳情。披差於周二向員工發表聲明，指曾聽許多員工談及職場上的不恰當行為，對此及對員工造成的痛苦深感抱歉。他承認Google長期存在職場性騷擾問題，2年來解僱48名員工，包括13名高級行政人員。<br />\n<br />\n根據《紐約時報》的報道，一名年輕女工程師在見工時，德沃爾宣稱自己與太太都是「多邊戀」，並邀請對方出席一場節日活動。女事主聲稱在活動上，德沃爾要求她脫去上衣接受「背部按摩」，她起初拒絕，但由於德沃爾堅持，最終只好讓對方按摩頸部。<br />\n<br />\n該名女工程師於數周後收到通知，指她不獲聘請，但未有給予解釋。女事主於事發後2年，向Google人事部門通報事件，對方指正在處理，但要求她保持沉默。直至傳媒最近在報道披露有關德沃爾的性侵指控後，女事主才公開事件；德沃爾其後公開道歉，承認自己判斷出錯。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle部分女員工不滿公司向涉性侵的Android前主管魯賓支付離職費，號召於周四（11月1日）大遊行抗議。魯賓的發言人回覆傳媒查詢時，否認當事人涉性侵而離職，他是為創業才離開公司。Google亦公開披差另一封發給員工的聲明指，沒有涉性侵而離職的人士獲離職費，聲言會為員工提供安全及有包容性的工作環境，承諾調查每宗性騷擾指控。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2DgmMzO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2DgmMzO&d=J6RhEfzMus7NitM9hdRZVDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=94158a1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2DgmMzO</a>"},{"pid":"e38cff206fc8b7f7272502985eab473c1a1e0d88","tid":886003,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T19:15:46.000Z","msg":"Don't be evil"},{"pid":"8e60843d7b5e671ee3d4dce33c0374d87b1745ad","tid":886003,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T19:51:42.000Z","msg":"Dragonfly: 咩事都無"},{"pid":"77898d947abcc3a2bbdface3a73b2035ac99a43b","tid":886003,"uid":64457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e38cff206fc8b7f7272502985eab473c1a1e0d88","tid":886003,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T19:15:46.000Z","msg":"Don't be evil"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T20:05:32.000Z","msg":"Google: except me"},{"pid":"f3f6bdb84a1fae475e0b965a724297d19d3f1331","tid":886003,"uid":11598,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T20:05:42.000Z","msg":"Google 變咗好多年啦<br />\n而家連CEO都係叉仔，左膠氾濫<br />\n又想返支那吸金 冇骨氣 垃圾公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5279d5715949818395cebf6696501f6acb71788e","tid":886003,"uid":146243,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T20:07:29.000Z","msg":"見工嗰陣 人地要求 然後自己除衫 同意比人按<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n好心個男人就請咗佢啦抽完水<br />\n而家有汗出冇糧出 唔發爛渣就奇<br />\n如果請咗咪ok 無問題 條女要升職嗰陣你按多幾次都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd082d13be1af8badebf172ae38465c49cf3e8d6","tid":886003,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T20:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YppdsHe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYppdsHe.jpg&h=426fa994&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ecb32e39810cd0c60eb6da62b8160bf2179b197","tid":886003,"uid":3549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:02:35.000Z","msg":"女事主聲稱在活動上，德沃爾要求她脫去上衣接受「背部按摩」，她起初拒絕，但由於德沃爾堅持，最終只好讓對方按摩頸部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092c5e9e186c871df6281a1bf7fddc5fcbdbd35c","tid":886003,"uid":34530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:07:03.000Z","msg":"香港Google員工，要返工不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27a8c7b7db450c39499362494ef643af8022ccf","tid":886003,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"092c5e9e186c871df6281a1bf7fddc5fcbdbd35c","tid":886003,"uid":34530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:07:03.000Z","msg":"香港Google員工，要返工不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港員工是google的忠實戰友"},{"pid":"3b9d795d203dcabaa8f651ee4f7ee8110f5d0d23","tid":886003,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"092c5e9e186c871df6281a1bf7fddc5fcbdbd35c","tid":886003,"uid":34530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:07:03.000Z","msg":"香港Google員工，要返工不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:12:23.000Z","msg":"我相信會好勤力咁扮工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遊行？不了"},{"pid":"08f5429c8423a43619816a7fcee8b3a2810cb419","tid":886003,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T08:50:32.000Z","msg":"香港人入左gooele點會唔聽話？"},{"pid":"13ec89c41fd977bbb8f29572527d621695a2495a","tid":886003,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b9d795d203dcabaa8f651ee4f7ee8110f5d0d23","tid":886003,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"092c5e9e186c871df6281a1bf7fddc5fcbdbd35c","tid":886003,"uid":34530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:07:03.000Z","msg":"香港Google員工，要返工不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:12:23.000Z","msg":"我相信會好勤力咁扮工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遊行？不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8bd4fb222fb74827e96d398d293fc7cb881c0a","tid":886003,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"搏炒？"}]}